(7, 1, '2014-01-09 00:00:48', '2014-01-08 22:00:48', '<span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">Plasele sudae sunt fabricate prin sudarea barelor de o</span></span><span style="font-size: small;">ț</span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">el suprapuse perpendicular una fa</span></span><span style="font-size: small;">ță</span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"> de alta prin sudur</span></span><span style="font-size: small;">ă</span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"> în puncte cu ajutorul unor aparate speciale. Se vinde in baloturi sau rulouri.</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">Plasele sudate fac parte din gama produselor metalurgice, utilizate </span></span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">în lucr</span></span><span style="font-size: small;">ă</span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ri de construc</span></span><span style="font-size: small;">ț</span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ii (fabricarea partoselelor industriale, armarea </span></span><span style="font-size: small;">ş</span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">apelor , la efectuarea lucrarilor de hidro si termoizolare , lucrari de zidarie</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">. O utilizare secundara a plaselor sudate o constituie folosirea acestora pentru imprejmuiri precum si in diverse confectii metalice.</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">Firma noastra produce plase cu diametrul barei de sarma de la Ø3 mm – Ø5 mm(la comanda producem plase cu diametrul barei de 6mm). Dimensiunile ochiurilor intre bare poate fi de 50 x 50; 100 x 100; 150 x 150; 200 x 200 mm. Dimensiunile de fabricatie ale panoului de plasa sudata sunt 1000x2000; 1000x3000; 2000x3000mm </span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">La cerere se pot executa plase sudate si cu alte dimensiuni de panou si ochiuri.</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">Cum se determina calitatea plasei sudate ?</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">Deoarece acest produs este folosit ca material de baz</span></span><span style="font-family: Segoe UI,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ă</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"> în multe tipuri de lucr</span></span><span style="font-family: Segoe UI,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ă</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ri de construc</span></span><span style="font-family: Segoe UI,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ț</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ii , alegerea corecta este de o importan</span></span><span style="font-family: Segoe UI,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ță</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"> capital</span></span><span style="font-family: Segoe UI,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ă</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">În primul rând , se examineaza cu aten</span></span><span style="font-family: Segoe UI,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ț</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ie sudura firelor longitudinale </span></span><span style="font-family: Segoe UI,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ș</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">i transversale . </span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">A doua caracteristic</span></span><span style="font-family: Segoe UI,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ă</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"> important</span></span><span style="font-family: Segoe UI,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ă</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"> –grosimea barei de sirma. Acesta ar trebui s</span></span><span style="font-family: Segoe UI,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ă</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"> fie la fel peste tot </span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">A treia component</span></span><span style="font-family: Segoe UI,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ă</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"> - marj</span></span><span style="font-family: Segoe UI,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ă</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"> de siguran</span></span><span style="font-family: Segoe UI,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ță</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"> . Sudura ochiurilor de plas</span></span><span style="font-family: Segoe UI,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ă</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"> ar trebui , sa reziste fara nici o dificultate la actiuni fizice </span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">A patra componenta – marimea ochiulor </span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">A cincea componenta – geometria panoului de plasa sudata, </span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">Ei bine , desigur , nu uita</span></span><span style="font-family: Segoe UI,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ț</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">i c</span></span><span style="font-family: Segoe UI,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ă</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"> orice material de calitate trebuie s</span></span><span style="font-family: Segoe UI,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ă</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"> fie înso</span></span><span style="font-family: Segoe UI,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ț</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ite de documentele relevante : certificate de calitate</span></span>', 'Ce este plasa armata', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ce-este-plasa-armata', '', '', '2014-01-22 21:07:37', '2014-01-22 19:07:37', '', 0, 'http://armesh.loc/?p=7', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(8, 1, '2014-01-09 00:00:48', '2014-01-08 22:00:48', '', 'Ce este plasa armata', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '7-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-09 00:00:48', '2014-01-08 22:00:48', '', 7, 'http://armesh.loc/?p=8', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(10, 1, '2014-01-09 00:01:20', '2014-01-08 22:01:20', 'ARMESH are la baza o echipa tanara si dinamica care si-a propus sa dezvolte un business serios in domeniul fabricarii si distributiei produselor din sarma. Ne-am pus ca scop sa producem numai produse de o calitate net superioara celora ce sunt pe piata de desfacere.\r\nDorim sa ne dezvoltam productia si pe alte produse , urmand sa mai acizitionam si alte utilaje. Ne distribuim produsele in mare parte in orasul Chisinau si zonele vecine. Urmeaza sa mai achizitionam si mijloace de transport pentru a raspunde mai bine la nevoile clientilor. In cazul in care clientul totusi doreste ca produsul sa fie transportat pina la destinatie NOI vom organiza mijlocul de transport.\r\nNoi consideram ca o firma poate creste doar prin calitatea si corectitudinea produselor comercializate , lucru pe care l-am facut si pe care intentionem sa il facem continuare.', 'Despre Companie', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'despre-companie', '', '', '2014-02-17 10:23:28', '2014-02-17 08:23:28', '', 0, 'http://armesh.loc/?page_id=10', 0, 'page', '', 0),
