serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"> ar trebui , sa reziste fara nici o dificultate la actiuni fizice </span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">A patra componenta – marimea ochiulor </span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">A cincea componenta – geometria panoului de plasa sudata, </span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">Ei bine , desigur , nu uita</span></span><span style="font-family: Segoe UI,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ț</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">i c</span></span><span style="font-family: Segoe UI,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ă</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"> orice material de calitate trebuie s</span></span><span style="font-family: Segoe UI,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ă</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"> fie înso</span></span><span style="font-family: Segoe UI,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ț</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial Rounded MT Bold,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">ite de documentele relevante : certificate de calitate</span></span>', 'Ce este plasa sudată', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '44-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-22 21:09:18', '2014-01-22 19:09:18', '', 44, 'http://armesh.loc/?p=45', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
